2:T7f4,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Mutable AI better than Windsurf (Codeium)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Mutable AI scores 6.0 overall while Windsurf (Codeium) scores 8.0. Mutable AI is best for auto-generating documentation and codebase understanding, while Windsurf (Codeium) excels for budget-conscious developers and teams wanting free AI autocomplete."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Mutable AI or Windsurf (Codeium)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Mutable AI starts at $12/mo and Windsurf (Codeium) starts at $10/mo. Mutable AI offers a free plan. Windsurf (Codeium) offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Mutable AI to Windsurf (Codeium)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Mutable AI and Windsurf (Codeium) support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Mutable AI vs Windsurf (Codeium)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Mutable AI holds an overall rating of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Windsurf (Codeium) has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Mutable AI for auto-generates wiki from code and Windsurf (Codeium) for generous free tier for individuals."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Mutable AI or Windsurf (Codeium)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Windsurf (Codeium) for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Mutable AI remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize auto-generates wiki from code. T