7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Mutable AI and Windsurf (Codeium) share a solid foundation of core features including Code Generation, Refactoring, Multi Language, Chat. Where Mutable AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Documentation, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Windsurf (Codeium) uniquely offers Autocomplete and Debugging and Ide Integration, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Mutable AI holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Windsurf (Codeium) scores 8/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Windsurf (Codeium) comes in at a lower starting price of $10/mo, while Mutable AI begins at $12/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Mutable AI's free tier and Windsurf (Codeium)'s free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
