b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Mutable AI is best suited for auto generating documentation, codebase understanding, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Windsurf (Codeium), meanwhile, shines for budget conscious developers, teams wanting free AI autocomplete, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2021, Mutable AI describes itself as \"AI-accelerated software development and documentation.\" Windsurf (Codeium), established in 2022, positions itself as \"AI-powered coding assistant with a generous free tier.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Windsurf (Codeium)** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 6.0), more features (7 vs 5), more competitive pricing, availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Mutable AI is a poor choice — far from it. Mutable AI excels in its own right, particularly for auto generating documentation and codebase understanding.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value generous free tier for individuals, go with Windsurf (Codeium). If auto-generates wiki from code matters more to you, Mutable AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
